+=============================================================================+
|                               Animal Crossing                               |
|                               Bell Calculator                               |
+=============================================================================+
| This is a way to find out how many bells you will get from selling bugs and |
| fish to the Nooklings in Animal Crossing: New Horizons! This is no more than|
| a glorified multiplication calculator.                                      |
+=============================================================================+
|                                  Features:                                  |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| - Can search up any fish                                                    |
| - Can search up any bug                                                     |
+=============================================================================+
|                                  Planned:                                   |
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| - Add CJ bonus                                                              |
| - Add Drop-off box "bonus"                                                  |
| - Implement a way to add multiple bugs/fish and not just one                |
+=============================================================================+